<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>259</hymn_number>
<key>Eb</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Tah nih a ka khamh lo, Mit-thli tla len hmanhsehlaw, Ka thinphan a dai
 kho lo, Ka sual cia tawl kho lo, Tah nih a ka khamh lo.

[C1]
   Jesuh a tap keimah ca'h, Jesuh thi cang thing cungah, Thlah awkah a
   kan hngah ko, Amah lawng a khamh kho.

[V2]
 Tuan nih a ka khamh lo, Rian tha bik tuan hmanh ninglaw, Ruah thatnak
 ka ngeih zongah, Ka thla an tharter kho lo, Tuan nih a ka khamh lo.

[C2]
   Jesuh a tap keimah ca'h, Jesuh thi cang thing cungah, Thlah awkah a
   kan hngah ko, Amah lawng a khamh kho.

[V3]
 Hngah nih a ka khamh lo, zaangnem sualnak a tampi, Zaangfah in a ka
 auh lio, Hngah ahcun thihnak a si, Hngah nih a ka khamh lo.

[C3]
   Jesuh a tap keimah ca'h, Jesuh thi cang thing cungah, Thlah awkah a
   kan hngah ko, Amah lawng a khamh kho.

[V4]
 Zumhnak in a khamh lai, Na Fa tap kan zumhter tuah, Amah tuahser
 bochan in, Vancung khua kan phak khawhnak, Zumhnak in a khamh lai.

[C4]
   Jesuh a tap keimah ca'h, Jesuh thi cang thing cungah, Thlah awkah a
   kan hngah ko, Amah lawng a khamh kho.</lyrics>
<title>TAH NIH A KA KHAMH LO CH259</title>
</song>